that we're assigned together.

333
00:15:16,380 --> 00:15:17,780
How about we find a time

334
00:15:17,780 --> 00:15:18,990
to discuss with Dong Huixin?

335
00:15:22,880 --> 00:15:24,860
If she hadn't just turned off
the air conditioner

336
00:15:24,900 --> 00:15:25,950
before consulting us,

337
00:15:26,020 --> 00:15:27,820
I wouldn't have
picked a fight like this.

338
00:15:28,190 --> 00:15:29,140
Besides, she's stubborn

339
00:15:29,190 --> 00:15:30,110
and unsociable.

340
00:15:30,310 --> 00:15:31,590
No one can persuade her.

341
00:15:31,990 --> 00:15:33,590
Besides attending classes and sleeping,

342
00:15:33,620 --> 00:15:34,990
can you find her?

343
00:15:41,740 --> 00:15:42,230
Top...

344
00:15:47,860 --> 00:15:48,380
Top...

345
00:15:50,140 --> 00:15:50,900
Top Student.

346
00:15:51,020 --> 00:15:51,780
Top Student.

347
00:16:02,470 --> 00:16:04,110
We'll do it ourselves.

348
00:16:04,430 --> 00:16:05,140
It's okay.

349
00:16:11,310 --> 00:16:11,900
Waitress.

350
00:16:12,780 --> 00:16:13,380
Come here.

351
00:16:13,430 --> 00:16:14,140
Go ahead.

352
00:16:14,140 --> 00:16:15,110
