whether it's fresh after eating it.

365
00:16:36,300 --> 00:16:37,060
Can you settle this?

366
00:16:37,070 --> 00:16:38,350
Call your store manager over.

367
00:16:38,420 --> 00:16:39,820
If not, get the person in charge.

368
00:16:39,840 --> 00:16:40,430
Sorry.

369
00:16:40,470 --> 00:16:41,710
