380
00:16:59,260 --> 00:16:59,900
Yeah.

381
00:16:59,960 --> 00:17:01,440
If it doesn't taste good, why eat it?

382
00:17:01,500 --> 00:17:01,990
Your squid

383
00:17:01,990 --> 00:17:03,260
