384
00:17:03,460 --> 00:17:04,540
That guy's still eating.

385
00:17:05,710 --> 00:17:06,230
Put it down.

386
00:17:08,020 --> 00:17:09,100
What a lousy place.

387
00:17:10,150 --> 00:17:10,630
Wait.

388
00:17:12,470 --> 00:17:13,100
Forget it.

389
00:17:13,630 --> 00:17:15,150
Sorry. Well...

390
00:17:16,060 --> 00:17:16,780
I'll pay the bill.

391
00:17:17,150 --> 00:17:17,740
This way.

392
00:17:18,880 --> 00:17:20,340
Why are you still eating? Let's go.

393
00:17:22,300 --> 00:17:23,190
Sorry, everyone.

394
00:17:23,300 --> 00:17:23,820
Well...

395
00:17:23,870 --> 00:17:24,990
