408
00:18:28,340 --> 00:18:29,020
Yeah.

409
00:18:29,300 --> 00:18:30,820
We're not that afraid of heat.

410
00:18:31,060 --> 00:18:32,470
Turning the fan on feels the same.

411
00:18:33,580 --> 00:18:34,950
I know you mean well.

412
00:18:35,260 --> 00:18:37,340
But there's no need to force yourselves

413
00:18:37,390 --> 00:18:38,190
for me.

414
00:18:38,630 --> 00:18:39,710
It won't be fair.

415
00:18:42,950 --> 00:18:44,100
How about this?

416
00:18:44,190 --> 00:18:45,100
You get up early.

417
00:18:45,150 --> 00:18:45,870
