422
00:18:52,060 --> 00:18:52,870
Isn't that fair?

423
00:18:53,630 --> 00:18:54,870
What do you think?

424
00:18:56,190 --> 00:18:57,230
I have no objection.

425
00:18:58,500 --> 00:18:59,470
I fully agree.

426
00:19:02,190 --> 00:19:03,540
That might not be a good idea.

427
00:19:03,780 --> 00:19:04,430
Top Student.

428
00:19:04,430 --> 00:19:05,300
Please don't move out.

429
00:19:05,390 --> 00:19:07,470
