449
00:20:05,710 --> 00:20:07,630
We'll take showers together soon.

450
00:20:18,340 --> 00:20:19,230
Close the door!

451
00:20:20,780 --> 00:20:21,540
Wait.

452
00:20:22,230 --> 00:20:22,990
You...

453
00:20:23,020 --> 00:20:23,710
Hurry up.

454
00:20:24,180 --> 00:20:24,820
Make the call.

455
00:20:24,820 --> 00:20:25,660
Are you going to call?

456
00:20:25,660 --> 00:20:26,220
Call him.

457
00:20:26,220 --> 00:20:26,780
Make the call.

458
00:20:26,780 --> 00:20:27,580
It's too late today.

459
00:20:27,580 --> 00:20:28,390
I'll call tomorrow.

460
00:20:28,440 --> 00:20:29,440
You're not going to call?

461
00:20:29,470 --> 00:20:31,060
Take it off!

462
00:20:33,230 --> 00:20:34,630
I'm a good woman!

463
00:20:34,700 --> 00:20:36,240
It's too late to say anything now.

464
00:20:36,300 --> 00:20:37,190
I like good women.

465
00:20:37,470 --> 00:20:38,390
Search for her phone!

466
00:20:43,580 --> 00:20:44,470
(That night,)

467
00:20:44,740 --> 00:20:45,630
(Dorm 401)

468
00:20:45,870 --> 00:20:47,340
(is finally all here)

469
00:20:47,430 --> 00:20:48,660
(during non-sleeping hours.)

470
00:20:49,150 --> 00:20:50,540
(We rearranged the seniority)

471
00:20:50,710 --> 00:20:51,910
(according to age.)

472
00:20:52,580 --> 00:20:53,150
(Huixin)

473
00:20:53,500 --> 00:20:55,300
(is the oldest.)

474
00:20:55,910 --> 00:20:56,990
(Little Princess Qiu Li)

475
00:20:57,390 --> 00:20:59,630
(claimed being the second oldest
with a look of disdain.)

476
00:20:59,640 --> 00:21:00,920
(It's a ranking that combines)

477
00:21:00,940 --> 00:21:02,430
