504
00:22:02,190 --> 00:22:02,820
Wontons.

505
00:22:08,470 --> 00:22:09,150
Huan'er.

506
00:22:09,340 --> 00:22:11,100
I know you've been tired from training,

507
00:22:11,100 --> 00:22:11,630
but

508
00:22:11,630 --> 00:22:13,260
