530
00:23:11,990 --> 00:23:13,060
I'm not talking about you.

531
00:23:16,470 --> 00:23:17,990
(Has Dahuang eaten?)

532
00:23:26,470 --> 00:23:28,990
(Yes, he enjoyed it.)

533
00:23:37,710 --> 00:23:38,190
