554
00:24:26,260 --> 00:24:27,870
In terms of the party's entertainment,

555
00:24:27,950 --> 00:24:29,580
students prefer
street dance performances

556
00:24:29,740 --> 00:24:30,500
and skits.

557
00:24:31,300 --> 00:24:32,780
From a spiritual perspective,

558
00:24:32,800 --> 00:24:34,440
traditional Chinese
music performances

559
00:24:34,460 --> 00:24:36,820
and poetry recitations will
allow the students to gain more.

560
00:24:39,190 --> 00:24:39,910
Arts Department

561
00:24:39,990 --> 00:24:41,480
lacks manpower for their performance.

562
00:24:41,480 --> 00:24:43,190
Since Sports Department
isn't participating,

563
00:24:43,190 --> 00:24:44,540
