564
00:24:45,740 --> 00:24:46,430
Jing Xichi.

565
00:24:46,710 --> 00:24:47,500
Come with me.

566
00:24:48,990 --> 00:24:49,580
No.

567
00:24:53,300 --> 00:24:55,500
This party is a joint performance
of all departments

568
00:24:55,580 --> 00:24:56,440
