580
00:26:04,340 --> 00:26:05,500
I gave it more thought.

581
00:26:06,540 --> 00:26:07,780
We must continue

582
00:26:08,020 --> 00:26:09,480
our martial arts performance.

583
00:26:09,520 --> 00:26:10,340
Didn't Du Wei say

584
00:26:10,390 --> 00:26:11,800
that our performances are outdated,

